The tiddlers with tag `Colleague` is used to filter authors for publication. 


----


<$link to="$:/config/tw-connector/authoring/expired-days">Expired Days Author's Publication</$link> 

<$edit-text tiddler="$:/config/tw-connector/authoring/expired-days" default="30" tag="input" />


The author's publication will be retrieved after expired days.

----

!! Homepage

The field `url` in the tiddlers with tag `Colleague` is used to to retrieve author's publications. All DOIs in the homepage is assumed as author's publications.


----
<$link to="$:/config/tw-connector/authoring/homepage/enable">Retrieve Publication from Homepage</$link> 

<$checkbox tiddler="$:/config/tw-connector/authoring/homepage/enable" field="text" checked="enable" unchecked="disable" default="enable"><$link to="$:/config/tw-connector/authoring/homepage/enable">Enable Homepage</$link></$checkbox>


----
!! Web of Science

The field `researcherid` in the tiddlers with tag `Colleague` is used to to retrieve author's publications. 

----
<$link to="$:/config/tw-connector/authoring/wos/enable">Retrieve Publication from Web of Science</$link> 

<$checkbox tiddler="$:/config/tw-connector/authoring/wos/enable" field="text" checked="enable" unchecked="disable" default="enable"><$link to="$:/config/tw-connector/authoring/wos/enable">Enable Web of Science</$link></$checkbox>

